Title: A Lower Bound on the Size of Algebraic Decision Trees for the MAX Problem  
Author: Dima Grigoriev Marek Karpinski Andrew Yao 
Note: 16802. Supported in part by  Research partially done while visiting the  Research supported in part by DFG Grant KA 673/4-1, by the ESPRIT Grants 7097 and EC-US 030, and by the Volkswagen-Stiftung.  08544. Research supported in part by NSF Grant CCR-9301430.  
